entry.string: Please select a cache key to be flushed.
entry.translation: Pleese-a select a ceche-a key tu be-a flooshed.

entry.string: All cached files of output associated with this key will be deleted.
entry.translation: Ell ceched feeles ooff ooootpoot essuceeeted veet thees key veell be-a deleted.

entry.string: You must select a cache key to flush. If there is no cache key to select the output cache is empty.
entry.translation: Yuoo moost select a ceche-a key tu floosh. Iff zeere-a is nu ceche-a key tu select zee ooootpoot ceche-a is impty.

entry.string: Cached #(1) files have been successfully flushed.
entry.translation: Ceched #(1) feeles hefe-a beee sooccessffoolly flooshed. Bork bork bork!

entry.string: Return to the cache key selector
entry.translation: Retoorn tu zee ceche-a key selectur
